# MambaIRv2-Pola++ (Lightweight SR, ×3 / ×4)

PolaFormer++ attention inside MambaIRv2-Light.

## Install

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python setup.py develop
```

## Train / Test

```bash
bash train.sh 3
bash train.sh 4
bash test.sh 3 /path/to/your_x3.pth
bash test.sh 4 /path/to/your_x4.pth
```

Configs: `options/train|test/mambairv2/*_x{3,4}.yml`  
No pretrained weights are shipped in this package.
